    <briefdescription>
<para>&lt; Exposed so sketches can call Joystick.button() etc. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Static singleton for the RP2040 DCS-BIOS / USB HID gateway.</para>
<para>Sets the USB VID/PID and product strings, initialises the Joystick HID composite device, and starts the UART link to <ref refid="namespacePanelBridge" kindref="compound">PanelBridge</ref> at 250000 baud. In <ref refid="namespaceSimGateway_1aa8f7b2f81634cf26fff1d4d03b3ec70b" kindref="member">loop()</ref>, drains the UART and dispatches 8-byte DIAG frames to registered callbacks. Sending ControlPackets to <ref refid="namespacePanelBridge" kindref="compound">PanelBridge</ref> is done via <ref refid="namespaceSimGateway_1a6211ad592ee4601e0b3f786c8c686c02" kindref="member">send()</ref>. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
